name: invite
value:
A command to invite this bot.
`<prefix>invite`

name: ping
value:
A command to check the latency between the bot server and your server.
`<prefix>ping`

name: help
value:
A command that brings up this dialogue.
`<prefix>help`

name: ascii
value:
A command that converts text to ascii.
`<prefix>ascii <Text>`

name: ascii-cyan
value:
A command that converts text to cyan colored ascii.
`<prefix>ascii-cyan <Text>`

name: ascii-gold
value:
A command that converts text to gold colored ascii.
`<prefix>ascii-gold <Text>`

name: prune-roles
value:
A command that deletes all the roles with the name `new role`.
`<prefix>prune-roles`

name: uptime
value:
A command that tells you the amount of time the bot has been up.
`<prefix>uptime`

name: emojify-channel
value:
A command that adds an emoji to the channel name, be warned you can only use emojify on a channel between 5 minute intervals.
`<prefix>emojify-channel <UnicodeEmoji>`
